# Server actions

`web/src/actions/[domain]/` — `verb-object.ts` + `verb-object.validation.ts`. Export `camelCaseAction`.

| Client | Use |
|--------|-----|
| `storeActionClient` | store admin (bound storeId) |
| `adminActionClient` | sys admin |
| `userRequiredActionClient` | account |
| `baseClient` | general |

- `"use server"` only on modules that export actions.
- Zod v4 schemas; `getUtcNow()` timestamps; logger on errors; transactions when needed.
- Create vs update: empty/null/`"new"` id → create.

Details: existing action files under `storeAdmin/tables/` as reference.
